{"type":"answer","id":285596,"parentType":"question","parentId":15697,"uid":8633,"contents":"如果对用橡皮子弹有疑问,不妨看看事后在全国开展的大搜捕。结合在一起大概可以合理推断这是蓄意的恐怖镇压。这写手法都是无产阶级专政写在俄共布简史(共产党员的圣经)里的教科书动作。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94?src=hashtag_click\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#六四知识问答</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%89%E9%97%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6?src=hashtag_click\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#天安门事件</a><br>\n<br>\n问：六四到底是什么？<br>\n<br>\nhttps://twitter.com/fb_china_today/status/1124167955607113728?s=20","date":"2020-06-08","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}